article.answer:
नया xml document बनाने के लिये : <br />
$xml = new DOMDocument('1.0', 'UTF-8');
        $root = $xml->createElement("article");
        $xml->appendChild($root);
foreach($entry as $key => $value ){
            $node = $xml->createElement($key);
            $node->nodeValue = $value;
            $root->appendChild($node);

        } <br />

यहाँ $entry एक associative array है । उसमे जो भी होगा वो xml document में भरा जायेगा । मेरा output ये रहा :
        
                  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<article>
<question>When did India get freedom?</question>
<answer>In 1947. India got freedom from British rule in 1947.</answer>
<location>burdwan</location>
<tags>India , history</tags>
<user>bittu</user>
<context>indian freedom</context>
<unixTime>1613583360</unixTime>
<date>17-02-2021</date>
</article>
